      "content": "thanks these are good. i'm a bit worried though, some of my regular customers are pretty conservative and might see \"social justice initiatives\" as a bit too political for just a coffee shop. can you give me some options that are a bit more subtle? maybe just focusing on the \"community\" aspect without using the buzzwords like DEI or social justice directly?",
