      "content": "those are better. i think the first one is the safest. i just want to make sure i'm not unintentionally offending anyone or looking like i'm taking a side in a culture war. do you think it's actually possible to be \"inclusive\" without it sounding like a political statement these days? or is that even a thing anymore?",
